{"word":"Abiezer","slug":"abiezer","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Abiezer</b> <a href=\"#/H44\">H44</a> <br/> 1. Called Jeezer, progenitor of the Abiezrites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=30'>Num 26:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=2'>Jos 17:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=34'>Jdg 6:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=2'>Jdg 8:2</a><br/> 2. One of David's heroes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=27'>2Sa 23:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=12'>1Ch 27:12</a>"}]}